Class PatchProcessSignaling

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public abstract class PatchProcessSignaling
extends PatchProcess
    Implementation of Process for cell metabolism.

    The PatchProcessSignaling process can be used for networks comprising a system of ODEs.
